{
  "text": "Monoclonal antibody-based sandwich direct ELISA MSD-ELISA was established and described in our previous reports [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , and the protocol is described in detail [CITATION_3] . In the present study, OD values over 0.1 were deemed positive.",
